### Variables (optional)
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api/v1
@contentType = application/json

### GET all posts
GET {{baseUrl}}/posts
Accept: application/json

###

### GET a specific post by ID (replace 1 with actual ID)
GET {{baseUrl}}/posts/1
Accept: application/json

###

### CREATE a new post
POST {{baseUrl}}/posts
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
    "title": "My First Post",
    "content": "This is the content of my first post."
}

###

### CREATE another post
POST {{baseUrl}}/posts
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
    "title": "Learning Go and Docker",
    "content": "Today I learned how to set up PostgreSQL in Docker and connect it to Go."
}

###

### CREATE a post with all fields
POST {{baseUrl}}/posts
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
    "title": "Advanced REST API",
    "content": "This post demonstrates a complete REST API with CRUD operations.",
    "author": "John Doe",
    "tags": ["go", "docker", "postgres"]
}

###

### UPDATE a post (replace 1 with actual ID)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/posts/1
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
    "title": "Updated Post Title",
    "content": "This is the updated content of the post."
}

###

### DELETE a post (replace 1 with actual ID)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/posts/1

###

### GET posts with query parameters
GET {{baseUrl}}/posts?limit=5&offset=0
Accept: application/json

###